{"tid":1535543,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"自制打狗棍","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:01:59.000Z","uid":16118,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8f54aef52cc57e009cadc3644bcf0f96a4e300de","tid":1535543,"uid":16118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:35:29.000Z","msg":"喺紐西蘭住咗幾年，由於住郊區，屋企附近有好多流浪狗，有流浪狗係好正常既一回事，但係d狗真係好撚惡，夜晚返屋企俾d狗見到又吠、又追、又咬，屌佢地老味，持住自己係狗就大撚晒<br />\n<br />\n自此我就diy咗一支平價打狗棍<br />\n材料包括有:<br />\n20mm燈喉  1條 $6<br />\n2寸鋼牙螺絲 一打 $5<br />\n<br />\n將條燈喉剪短，正常燈喉一條3m，咁我地只需要500mm，太長條燈喉有彈性唔夠硬淨，500mm-600mm就最撚fit， 視乎自己需要。<br />\n<br />\n之後將鋼牙螺絲修上條燈喉，想修幾多粒就視乎自己需要。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zePAGFs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzePAGFs.png&h=db2bd051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賣點就係夠平，又可以打走d狗，用完dum咗佢又唔肉赤<br />\n<br />\n打狗好啦 唔好攞黎打人"},{"pid":"5d7dc4d9ed77f568ba1528e37ec297bed578c256","tid":1535543,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530124</a>"},{"pid":"8b76435060f66fe677e633433aa77960763d834a","tid":1535543,"uid":299623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"唔夠硬"},{"pid":"1cce066e7f776c332bd33a0c8e96288bd84d9bf9","tid":1535543,"uid":16118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8b76435060f66fe677e633433aa77960763d834a","tid":1535543,"uid":299623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"唔夠硬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:40:07.000Z","msg":"的確 勝在輕便"},{"pid":"ae75fcd2285cb6df829d95d48372ddf9c15300a9","tid":1535543,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply